Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:22.35,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.5}Brave Shine　手を伸ばせばまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:27.71,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.5}Stay the night　傷だらけの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:36.91,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)\blur0.5}You save my life　かざした刃の先に想いを重ねた
